ADDITIONAL TERMS:

TONEBENCH is a procedural sound-effects synthesizer built on the Web Audio
API. All synthesis runs locally in the browser — there are no samples, audio
libraries, or external services involved. The core synthesis engine
(src/engine/tonebenchEngine.ts) is intentionally self-contained and may be
copied into other projects; such copies remain subject to this license.
